data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful residence nestled in a sought-after neighborhood. Impeccably maintained, this home awaits your arrival. Step into the elegant living space flowing seamlessly into the dining area and a charming eat-in kitchen. The dining room provides access to a powder room and the basement. The fully finished basement boasts a bonus room adjacent to the laundry area, offering a view of a stunning covered patio and expansive backyard. The meticulously landscaped outdoor space provides an idyllic setting for relaxation or hosting gatherings. Upstairs, three spacious bedrooms await. Conveniently situated near various shopping, dining, and transportation options. Don't miss the chance to make this home yours before it's gone.  Home comes with a transferable home warranty from American Preferred Home Warranty.
